            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <h2>常温 60 天保存</h2><p>周黑鸭新升级“60 天<strong>常温</strong>版”现已上市，官方定价 18 元 / 盒。</p><p>今日任选 3 盒仅需 29.7 元即可入手，单盒仅需 9.9 元：</p><dir class=""><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=213e04dc17785074646944229e0f72&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=C%2BtOjRPl7H2lhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJcSpXWKPbs5uRxs2pj2RztdP%2FE1%2B9jPY8BPYW1ljvGwH%2FvQlvE05zFhcUmRU2W5K6RSHvQe2jOLZ9pbNCYX0I%2BPP%2BWUTgK%2F%2B0DI9LnV2RxzN7CtXivpqDNXqqKMhEj%2BJ0qyHwQPWHy3Klb1EVyejktwJvhFCTE4y8tq9PiEi9ua7qC1ydbwJ6x%2Blxp4S%2BlOq9qbU66yYTUTnOb1nxo9CBhEPpMzUza%2Fkb7VUH29vhiVRKJFgimdBYZHg%2Fu3Aqy21CqdJTI101HEbqW9%2Fx9lGerFVusqqnhify&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1778507464@214142f8_28a6_19e174e4032_3a40@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.alicdn.com/i2/2221268563509/O1CN01SSRGii1bnAu097FP6_!!2221268563509.jpg" title="干净配料表：周黑鸭 60 天常温长保大升级，鸭脖 18 → 9.9 元 / 盒官方发车" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">周黑鸭 60 天常保升级装</span></span><span class="card-abstract">领 30 元券</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">任选 3 件 29.7 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">领 30 元券</span></span></span></span></a></dir><h2>低温 7 天保存</h2><p>周黑鸭・5 盒锁鲜装日常售价 64.9 元，今日实付 32.8 元包邮到手。</p><p>3 鸭脖 + 2 鸭翅，6.5 元 / 盒闭眼囤：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>先领 20 元券：<a href="https://coupon.m.jd.com/coupons/show.action?key=ccmec1s4o1a74d778423ed7fdcf08e55&amp;roleId=2316174804&amp;to" target="_blank">点此领券</a></p></li></ul><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/HGIrYcd" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/403374/4/16120/288227/69b8b6d2F9c246fbb/00833203206844d2.jpg" title="干净配料表：周黑鸭 60 天常温长保大升级，鸭脖 18 → 9.9 元 / 盒官方发车" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">周黑鸭 冷藏锁鲜装 5 盒</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> 3 盒鸭脖 2 盒鸭翅</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">券后 32.8 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>单盒折合仅需 6.56 元，<strong>鸭脖折合 24.3 元 / 斤，远低线下小摊</strong>。</p><h2>常温版简介</h2><blockquote><p>以“酱板鸭翅根（甜辣味）”为例，配料表为（具体以实物为准）：</p><p>鸭翅根、植物油、复合调味料、香辛料类、白砂糖、味精、鸡精调味料、食用盐、酿造酱油、调香白酒、食用香精香料。</p></blockquote><p>升级 60 天常温保存主要靠：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>高阻隔包装材料：采用铝箔 +PET 复合膜等 9 层高阻隔材质，氧气阻隔率达 99.5%，能隔绝外界氧气、水分和污染物，从包装层面阻断腐败源头。</p></li><li><p>精准气体置换：抽除包装内自然空气后，按 30% 二氧化碳 +70% 氮气的黄金比例充入气体，抑制需氧菌繁殖。</p></li></ul><p><img alt="c0262f3540e83ddb.jpg.avif" height="1050" src="https://img13.360buyimg.com/imgzone/jfs/t1/369958/8/6605/150777/6929699aFc1a525df/c0262f3540e83ddb.jpg" title="干净配料表：周黑鸭 60 天常温长保大升级，鸭脖 18 → 9.9 元 / 盒官方发车" width="790" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?traceId=213e04dc17785074646944229e0f72&amp;srItem=1&amp;e=C%2BtOjRPl7H2lhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJcSpXWKPbs5uRxs2pj2RztdP%2FE1%2B9jPY8BPYW1ljvGwH%2FvQlvE05zFhcUmRU2W5K6RSHvQe2jOLZ9pbNCYX0I%2BPP%2BWUTgK%2F%2B0DI9LnV2RxzN7CtXivpqDNXqqKMhEj%2BJ0qyHwQPWHy3Klb1EVyejktwJvhFCTE4y8tq9PiEi9ua7qC1ydbwJ6x%2Blxp4S%2BlOq9qbU66yYTUTnOb1nxo9CBhEPpMzUza%2Fkb7VUH29vhiVRKJFgimdBYZHg%2Fu3Aqy21CqdJTI101HEbqW9%2Fx9lGerFVusqqnhify&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1778507464@214142f8_28a6_19e174e4032_3a40@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.alicdn.com/i2/2221268563509/O1CN01SSRGii1bnAu097FP6_!!2221268563509.jpg" title="干净配料表：周黑鸭 60 天常温长保大升级，鸭脖 18 → 9.9 元 / 盒官方发车" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">周黑鸭 60 天常温保存升级装</span></span><span class="card-abstract">领 30 元券</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">任选 3 件 29.7 元</span><span class="card-btn-d